title: Lawmakers' probe of UK stockpicker and broking giant could shake up fund industry, analysts say
text: A post-mortem by British lawmakers and regulators into the suspension of the U.K.'s best known stockpicker's flagship fund could expose some systemic flaws in the fund industry, analysts suggest.

title: Terry Gou resigns as Foxconn’s chairman to run for president of Taiwan
text: Terry Gou said at Foxconn’s annual general meeting today that he is leaving the electronics manufacturing giant as he prepares to run for president of Taiwan.
